# Education Performance & Resource Allocation Dashboard

## Project Overview
This project analyzes education performance and resource allocation using interactive dashboard visualizations. It provides insights into student attendance, average marks, pass vs fail distribution, utilization percentage, and resource usage analysis for better academic planning and decision-making.
- education_performance_dataset.xlsx

## Tools Used
- Excel / Power BI
- GitHub

## Features
- Average Marks Analysis
- Attendance Tracking
- Pass vs Fail Distribution
- Resource Usage Analysis
- Utilization Percentage Monitoring
- Interactive Data Visualization

## Purpose
The dashboard helps educational institutions monitor student performance, analyze attendance trends, optimize resource allocation, and support data-driven academic decision-making through visual analytics.

